articles.author: Rebecca Rubin
articles.title: Box Office: ‘Black Phone 2’ Grabs $26.5 Million in Otherwise Muted October Weekend - Variety
articles.description: Universal and Blumhouse's horror sequel "Black Phone 2" kicked off spooky season with $26.5 million from 3,411 North American theaters.
articles.content: Universal and Blumhouse’s horror sequel “Black Phone 2” kicked off spooky season with $26.5 million from 3,411 North American theaters. Those ticket sales were enough to lead an otherwise sleepy week… [+6307 chars]
